    <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="effective-date">
            Last updated: July 19, 2025
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>This Privacy Policy ("Policy") describes how <strong>Shrey Bot</strong> (the "Bot", "we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, processes, stores, and protects your personal information when you use our Discord bot services.</p>
            
            <p>By using Shrey Bot, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal information as described herein.</p>

            <div class="important">
                <strong>Important:</strong> This Privacy Policy complies with applicable data protection laws including GDPR, India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act 2023, and Discord's Developer Policy.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>2. Data Controller Information</h2>
            <p>The data controller for your personal information is the operator of Shrey Bot:</p>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> New Delhi, Delhi, India</p>
                <p><strong>Governing Law:</strong> Laws of India</p>
                <p><strong>Contact:</strong> Available through appropriate Discord channels</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>3. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect and process the following categories of personal data to provide our bot services:</p>
            
            <div class="data-types">
                <h3>Automatically Collected Data:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Discord User ID:</strong> Your unique Discord identifier for command processing</li>
                    <li><strong>Discord Username:</strong> Your current Discord display name and tag</li>
                    <li><strong>Server Information:</strong> Discord server ID, name, and channel information where the bot operates</li>
                    <li><strong>Message Data:</strong> Content of messages when directly interacting with the bot</li>
                    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Commands used, timestamps, and interaction patterns</li>
                    <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> Error logs, performance metrics, and system information</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Data We Do NOT Collect:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Private messages not directed to the bot</li>
                    <li>Voice chat recordings</li>
                    <li>Email addresses or phone numbers</li>
                    <li>Payment or financial information</li>
                    <li>Files or attachments not sent to the bot</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
            <p>We process your personal data based on the following legal grounds:</p>
            
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Data Type</th>
                    <th>Legal Basis</th>
                    <th>Purpose</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>User IDs & Commands</td>
                    <td>Legitimate Interest</td>
                    <td>Providing bot functionality and services</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Server Data</td>
                    <td>Contract Performance</td>
                    <td>Operating within Discord servers</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Usage Analytics</td>
                    <td>Legitimate Interest</td>
                    <td>Improving bot performance and features</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Error Logs</td>
                    <td>Legitimate Interest</td>
                    <td>Debugging and system maintenance</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>5. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use your personal information for the following purposes:</p>
            
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Service Provision:</strong> To operate the bot and provide requested functionality</li>
                <li><strong>Command Processing:</strong> To understand and respond to user commands</li>
                <li><strong>Performance Monitoring:</strong> To ensure the bot operates efficiently and reliably</li>
                <li><strong>Security:</strong> To protect against abuse, spam, and unauthorized access</li>
                <li><strong>Improvement:</strong> To analyze usage patterns and enhance bot features</li>
                <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> To meet legal obligations and Discord's policies</li>
                <li><strong>Communication:</strong> To respond to user inquiries and provide support</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>6. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
            <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your data only in the following circumstances:</p>
            
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Discord Platform:</strong> Data shared through normal Discord API interactions</li>
                <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law, court order, or governmental authority</li>
                <li><strong>Safety:</strong> To protect the safety of users, the public, or our services</li>
                <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> With trusted partners who assist in operating our services (under strict confidentiality agreements)</li>
                <li><strong>Business Transfer:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="important">
                <strong>Data Transfers:</strong> Your data may be processed outside your country of residence. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place for international transfers as required by applicable law.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain your personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this policy:</p>
            
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Data Type</th>
                    <th>Retention Period</th>
                    <th>Reason</th>
